structure.unit: REINSURANCE, RECIPROCAL AND LLOYD'S PLAN INSURANCE (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 105, sec. 21; and ch. 106, sec. 22, effective June 17, 1948. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 13; and ch. 100, sec. 15, effective October 1, 1947. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 743m-1, 743m-2, 743m-8, 743m-12.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Interinsurance or reciprocal contracts exchange; attorney to execute contracts.
